BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:siirtymä-ambient-festival-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260713T115347Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260630
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260701
SUMMARY:Deadline: Siirtymä Ambient Music Festival 2026: Open Call (Tampere
 \, Finland)
DESCRIPTION:Siirtymä Ambient Music Festival 2026 is a free\, community-dri
 ven festival in Tampere\, Finland\, organised by Suomen Ambientyhdistys ry
  (Finnish Ambient Association). The festival uses overlapping simultaneous
  performances across multiple locations\, emphasising spatial and ambient 
 experience over traditional stage formats. Open to artists and collectives
  working in ambient music\, sound art\, spatial installations\, and interd
 isciplinary practices\; no career-stage restriction\; the festival priorit
 ises emerging and lesser-known artists. The 2026 theme focuses on strength
 ening diversity\, creating multiple voices\, and finding new ways to encou
 nter one another and the urban environment. Technical support is provided 
 to selected participants. No travel or accommodation funding is publicly c
 onfirmed. NOTE: deadline of June 30 is from the Community Arts Network PDF
 \; verify at https://siirtyma.com/en/siirtym-2026 before submitting. Conta
 ct Suomen Ambientyhdistys ry directly for application details.\n\nOrganisa
 tion: Suomen Ambientyhdistys ry (Finnish Ambient Association)\nLocation: T
 ampere\, Finland (multiple simultaneous venues\, site-specific)\nAward: Te
 chnical support provided. No artist fee publicly confirmed. No application
  fee.\nDuration: Festival date: 5 September 2026.\n\nMore: https://siirtym
 a.com/en/siirtym-2026?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=ref
 erral
